{{> layout/header}}

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/booking/bookingSuccess.css">

<div class="container">
    <div class="success-container">
        <span class="success-icon">🎉</span>
        <h2 style="font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px;">결제 완료!</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">
            예약이 성공적으로 확정되었습니다.<br>
            어울림 대여공간을 이용해주셔서 감사합니다.
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">예약코드</span>
                <span class="info-value"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">결제금액</span>
                <span class="info-value"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">인원</span>
                <span class="info-value"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">인원</span>
                <span class="info-value">장소 - 공간</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">대여시간</span>
                <span class="info-value">장소 - 공간</span>
            </div>
            <div class="email-alert">
                📧 입장용 <strong>QR코드</strong>를 {{user.email}}로 발송했습니다.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="/user/bookings" class="custom-btn btn-fill">내 예약 확인하기</a>
            <a href="/" class="custom-btn btn-outline">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{> layout/footer}}